node.title: Two badly injured in Manukau crash
node.description: Motorists are asked to avoid the area.
node.content: ["Two people have been badly injured in a \"serious crash\" in south Auckland, police say.", "Emergency services are responding to the single-vehicle crash, which happened on Everglade Dr in Goodwood Heights, Manukau.", "The crash was reported to police at about 11:15am on Christmas Day.", "\"Two people are reported to be seriously injured,\" a police spokesperson said.", "\"The road is blocked and motorists are asked to avoid the area.\""]
